{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be vibrant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e0f2ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-bg: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: var(--primary-color) 3px solid;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.8), rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.6)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/007bff/ffffff?text=SecureGuard') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Digital Fortress</h2>\n            <p>Protecting your business from evolving cyber threats with cutting-edge solutions and expert insights.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Comprehensive Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h4>Threat Detection & Prevention</h4>\n                    <p>Proactive monitoring and advanced tools to identify and neutralize threats before they impact your business.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield\"></i>\n                    <h4>Risk Assessment & Management</h4>\n                    <p>Thorough analysis of your vulnerabilities and strategic planning to mitigate potential cyber risks.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h4>Data Security & Encryption</h4>\n                    <p>Ensuring your sensitive data is protected with robust encryption and access control measures.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-file-contract\"></i>\n                    <h4>Compliance & Auditing</h4>\n                    <p>Navigating complex regulatory landscapes and ensuring your operations meet industry standards.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                    <h4>Security Awareness Training</h4>\n                    <p>Empowering your employees with the knowledge to recognize and respond to cyber threats.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h4>Incident Response Planning</h4>\n                    <p>Developing clear, actionable plans to effectively manage and recover from security breaches.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Why Choose SecureGuard?</h3>\n            <p>At SecureGuard, we combine deep industry expertise with a relentless commitment to protecting your digital assets. We understand that every business is unique, and we tailor our solutions to meet your specific needs, ensuring peace of mind in an increasingly complex cyber world.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Email: info@secureguard.com | Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}